    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rivers, streams, creeks, or any other type of watercourses that formerly existed but no longer do, or that currently exist for some distance but then disappear into an underground channel or dry up in an arid area.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
